===Etymology===
From both the {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{m|la|acadēmicus}} and the {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|académique|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|academia|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἀκαδημικός|tr=akademeikos|lang=grc}}, from {{term|Ἀκαδημία|tr=Akademia||the location where Plato taught|lang=grc}} (alternative form: {{term|Ἀκαδήμεια|lang=grc}}); compare {{term|academy|lang=en}}.<ref name=WI3>{{R:MW3 1976}}</ref>

